column8: ,Frequently Asked Questions about our Training Videos:","&nbsp
column17: ,Do I need any prerequisite skills to watch this video training?","&nbsp
column21: ,No. We've designed our training videos to be easy to understand and follow so you should be able to work along with the trainer just fine.","&nbsp
column42: ,Can I download this video to my computer?","&nbsp
column46: ,Yes. This Video is a Windows Media Video (.wmv) file. It is zipped up ready to download to your computer. There is no streaming of the video just download it straight to your computer so you can enjoy it over and over.","&nbsp
column54: ,How soon do I get access to the training videos?","&nbsp
column58: ,As soon as you have paid you will get immediate access to begin downloading this Training Video.","&nbsp
column71: ,Of course. You can click on the All Training Videos link on this page and browse for single training videos. Or you can use the Search feature located at the top of each page.","&nbsp
